      "CancerType": "Non-small Cell Lung Cancer",
      "DOI": "10.7937/k9/tcia.2015.npgzyzbz",
      "Description": "<p>\n\tThe Computed tomography (CT) Image data was obtained on patients diagnosed with Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) with mixed stage &amp; histology from the H. Lee Moffitt Cancer Center and Research Institute. Scans were obtained from patients who underwent surgical resection and had corresponding pre-surgery diagnostic CTs.</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\tPlease see the <a href=\"\" url=\"https://doi.org/10.7937/K9/TCIA.2015.NPGZYZBZ\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#external-web-warning\" class=\"external-link\">QIN LUNG CT <i class=\"fa-solid fa-external-link external-link-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></a>  page to learn more about the images and to obtain any supporting metadata for this collection.</p>\n",
